author: Sarah Burns
title: Coronavirus: Seapoint, Sandycove and Forty Foot bathing spots closed
description: Council says move taken in interests of public health and ‘to align with Covid-19 restrictions’
content:
Dublin bathing spots Seapoint, Sandycove and the Forty Foot have been closed to the public until further notice.
